    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, RtSpecification

    public class RtSpecificationImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements RtSpecification
    An implementation of the model object 'Rt Specification'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Utility
    • Occ Kind
    • TRef
    • Rel Dl
    • Abs Dl
    • Bound Dl
    • Rd Time
    • Miss
    • Priority
    • Base Comment
    • Context
